summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Tenth Avenue Northeast from East Sixty-fifth Street to Sylvester Place, in the City of Seattle, by grading & curbing under Ordinance No. 18244, creating Local Improvement District No. 1723 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
